 + Shock Mount + Table stand+Pop filter+ Wind foam+XLR to 3.5mm mic Cable +Y cable', '【Come with XLR to 3.5mm Balanced Cable】  Multipurpose Condenser Microphone comes with XLR to 3.5mm Balanced Cable, which can transmit more realistic sound, could eliminate signal loss, and blocks interference which may prevent the loss of sound quality. When your device (like a smartphone, PC, computer, camera, etc.) has an AUX (3.5mm or 1/8 inch) mic jack, or a 3.5mm combination jack of the microphone and headphone, this ZHENREN Condenser Microphone is suitable to choose from.']
